invalid type: string "\n### Use Case Name:\nKeyboard Navigation\n\n### Use Case ID:\n8\n\n### Field:\nDescription\n\n### Description:\nLearners can interact with the website using only a keyboard. This is a critical\nfeature for users relying on assistive technologies like Screen Readers\n(VoiceOver or NVDA).\n\n### Actor:\nLearner\n\n### Pre-Condition:\nUser has a keyboard device.\n\n\n’’’’’’’’’’